SQL_STMT_U.val: select count(*) from :1/DEBH DEBH, :1/DHIC DHIC where DEBH.DEBH_NO = DHIC.DHIC_DEBH and DHIC.DHIC_INFS_CODE = 'KV' and DEBH.DEBH_HADR_COUNTRY = 'NL' and DEBH.DEBH_LEGALOWNER_DEBH > 0 and DEBH.DEBH_LEGALOWNER_DEBH in ( Select DEBH_LEGALOWNER_DEBH from :1/DEBH DEBH, :1/DHIC DHIC where DEBH.DEBH_LEGALOWNER_DEBH > 0 and DEBH.DEBH_HADR_COUNTRY = 'NL' and DHIC.DHIC_DEBH = DEBH_NO and DHIC.DHIC_INFS_CODE = 'KV' group by DEBH.DEBH_LEGALOWNER_DEBH having min( left (DHIC.DHIC_ID, 8)) <> max( left (DHIC.DHIC_ID, 8)) )

select count(*) from :1/DEBH DEBH, :1/DHIC DHIC where DEBH.DEBH_NO = DHIC.DHIC_DEBH and DHIC.DHIC_INFS_CODE = 'KV' and DEBH.DEBH_HADR_COUNTRY = 'NL' and left(DHIC.DHIC_ID,8) in ( Select left (DHIC.DHIC_ID, 8) from :1/DEBH DEBH, :1/DHIC DHIC where DEBH.DEBH_HADR_COUNTRY = 'NL' and DHIC.DHIC_DEBH = DEBH.DEBH_NO and DHIC.DHIC_INFS_CODE = 'KV' group by left (DHIC.DHIC_ID, 8) having min( DEBH.DEBH_LEGALOWNER_DEBH)<> max( DEBH.DEBH_LEGALOWNER_DEBH) )

select count(*) from :1/DEBH DEBH, :1/DHIC DHICa where DEBH.DEBH_NO = DHICa.DHIC_DEBH and DHICa.DHIC_INFS_CODE in ('KV', 'EU', 'CO', 'AT', 'BE') and exists (select * from :1/DHIC DHICb where DHICb.DHIC_ID = DHICa.DHIC_ID and DHICb.DHIC_DEBH <> DHICa.DHIC_DEBH and DHICb.DHIC_INFS_CODE = DHICa.DHIC_INFS_CODE)

select count(*) from :1/DEBH DEBH, :1/DHIC DHICa where DEBH.DEBH_NO = DHICa.DHIC_DEBH and DHICa.DHIC_INFS_CODE in ('KV', 'EU', 'CO', 'AT', 'BE') and exists (select * from :1/DHIC DHICb where DHICb.DHIC_ID <> DHICa.DHIC_ID and DHICb.DHIC_DEBH = DHICa.DHIC_DEBH and DHICb.DHIC_INFS_CODE = DHICa.DHIC_INFS_CODE)
select count(*) from :1/DEBC DEBC where not exists (select * from :1/DEBH DEBH where DEBH.DEBH_NO = DEBC.DEBC_DEBH)
select count(*) from :1/DHIC DHIC where DHIC_INFS_CODE = '' or DHIC_ID = '' or not exists (select * from :1/DEBH DEBH where DEBH.DEBH_NO = DHIC.DHIC_DEBH )

select count(*) from :1/DEBC a where a.debc_datdeleted is null and debc_debc <> '0' and debc_debc <> '' and exists (select * from :1/debc b where b.debc_no <> a.debc_no and b.debc_admno = a.debc_admno and b.debc_clntno = a.debc_clntno and b.debc_debc = a.debc_debc and b.debc_datdeleted is null)

Header.Description: NL DEBH with dif. ID nr

SQL_STMT_U.val: select DEBH_NO, DEBH_HADR_NAME1, DEBH_HADR_CITY, DEBH_LEGALOWNER_DEBH, DHIC_ID from :1/DEBH DEBH, :1/DHIC DHIC where DEBH.DEBH_NO = DHIC.DHIC_DEBH and DHIC.DHIC_INFS_CODE = 'KV' and DEBH.DEBH_HADR_COUNTRY = 'NL' and DEBH.DEBH_LEGALOWNER_DEBH > 0 and DEBH.DEBH_LEGALOWNER_DEBH in ( Select DEBH_LEGALOWNER_DEBH from :1/DEBH DEBH, :1/DHIC DHIC where DEBH.DEBH_LEGALOWNER_DEBH > 0 and DEBH.DEBH_HADR_COUNTRY = 'NL' and DHIC.DHIC_DEBH = DEBH_NO and DHIC.DHIC_INFS_CODE = 'KV' group by DEBH.DEBH_LEGALOWNER_DEBH having min( left (DHIC.DHIC_ID, 8)) <> max( left (DHIC.DHIC_ID, 8)) ) order by DEBH.DEBH_LEGALOWNER_DEBH, DEBH.DEBH_NO for fetch only

SQL_STMT_U.val: select DEBH_NO, DEBH_HADR_NAME1, DEBH_HADR_CITY, DEBH_LEGALOWNER_DEBH, DHIC_ID , DHIC_INFS_CODE from :1/DEBH DEBH, :1/DHIC DHICa , :1/GSET GSET where GSET_ID = 226 and DEBH.DEBH_NO = DHICa.DHIC_DEBH and DHICa.DHIC_INFS_CODE in ('LN', GSET_INFSCODE, 'CO', 'AT', 'BE') and exists (select * from :1/DHIC DHICb where DHICb.DHIC_ID = DHICa.DHIC_ID and DHICb.DHIC_DEBH <> DHICa.DHIC_DEBH and DHICb.DHIC_INFS_CODE = DHICa.DHIC_INFS_CODE) order by DHIC_ID, DEBH_NO for fetch only

SQL_STMT_U.val: select DEBH_NO, DEBH_HADR_NAME1, DEBH_HADR_CITY, DEBH_LEGALOWNER_DEBH, DHIC_ID , DHIC_INFS_CODE from :1/DEBH DEBH, :1/DHIC DHICa , :1/GSET GSET where GSET_ID = 226 and DEBH.DEBH_NO = DHICa.DHIC_DEBH and DHICa.DHIC_INFS_CODE in ('KV',GSET_INFSCODE, 'CO', 'AT', 'BE') and exists (select * from :1/DHIC DHICb where DHICb.DHIC_ID <> DHICa.DHIC_ID and DHICb.DHIC_DEBH = DHICa.DHIC_DEBH and DHICb.DHIC_INFS_CODE = DHICa.DHIC_INFS_CODE) order by DEBH_NO, DHIC_ID for fetch only

SQL_STMT_U.val: select DEBC_ADMNO, DEBC_CLNTNO, DEBC_DEBC, DEBC_DEBH from :1/DEBC DEBC where not exists (select * from :1/DEBH DEBH where DEBH.DEBH_NO = DEBC.DEBC_DEBH) order by DEBC_ADMNO, DEBC_CLNTNO, DEBC_DEBC for fetch only

select DHIC_INFS_CODE, DHIC_ID, DHIC_DEBH from :1/DHIC DHIC where DHIC_INFS_CODE = '' or DHIC_ID = '' or not exists (select * from :1/DEBH DEBH where DEBH.DEBH_NO = DHIC.DHIC_DEBH ) order by DHIC_INFS_CODE, DHIC_ID, DHIC_DEBH for fetch only

select debc_no, debc_debh, debc_debc,debc_admno, debc_clntno from :1/DEBC a where a.debc_datdeleted is null and debc_debc <> '0' and debc_debc <> '' and exists (select * from :1/debc b where b.debc_no <> a.debc_no and b.debc_admno = a.debc_admno and b.debc_clntno = a.debc_clntno and b.debc_debc = a.debc_debc and b.debc_datdeleted is null) order by debc_admno, debc_clntno , debc_debc for fetch only
